1  Zedekia ne jahigni piero ariyo gachiel kane odoko ruodh Juda, kendo norito piny kuom higni apar gachiel, kodak Jerusalem. Min mare ne nyinge Hamutal nyar Jeremia ma ja-Libna. 
2  Timbe Zedekia ne richo e nyim Ruoth Nyasaye, mana kaka timbe Jehoyakim. 
3  Jo-Jerusalem gi jo-Juda nomiyo Ruoth Nyasaye mirima, nyaka nodarogi, motergi e tuech.

